org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.neo4j.dialect.impl

Class Neo4jAssociationQueries

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.neo4j.dialect.impl.Neo4jAssociationQueries

  • public class Neo4jAssociationQueries
extends Object
    Container for the queries related to one association family in Neo4j. Unfortunately, we cannot use the same queries for all associations, as Neo4j does not allow to parameterize on node labels which would be required, as the association table is stored as a label.
    Author:
    Davide D'Alto
